---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact – Annadel Builders Inc." description="Contact Annadel Builders Inc. for custom home building in Sonoma County. Call (707) 579-6282.">
  <PageHeader title="Contact" />

  <section class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg mb-8">Creating beautiful projects for our clients is more than our job—it's our passion. At Annadel Builders, Inc., our Napa County fine home builders approach each aspect of home building with methodology and care, from pre-construction through occupancy. In the initial pre-construction process, our team facilitates project price estimates, material research, assistance in obtaining the proper permits, scheduling, plans, and more.</p>

      <p class="mb-8">We work closely with each and every client to establish well-laid, comprehensive plans from the outset. We'd love to hear about your project and whether we can help you achieve your goals. Annadel Builders works with clients building home sites throughout the North Bay, including Sonoma, Napa, Marin, and Mendocino counties.</p>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl mb-6">Get In Touch</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p><strong>Annadel Builders Inc.</strong></p>
          <p>4010 Montecito Avenue<br />Santa Rosa, California 95409</p>
          <p>Phone: <a href="tel:7075796282" class="text-teal hover:underline">(707) 579-6282</a></p>
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@annadelbuildersinc.com" class="text-teal hover:underline">info@annadelbuildersinc.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
